My first attempt at a humanoid SCP.

Two notes: 

1) The detail about living in an empty condo without realizing it is based off a story I heard in the local news someone was literally sold a unit in an empty, maintenance-less building in Florida and lived there for weeks before realizing that something was off. Just in case I was stretching your credulity.

2) The detail about the bus stop is also true something I heard about on NPR. It has apparently proven to be an effective means of calming patients with Alzheimer's disease at assisted living facilities, when they grow agitated and attempt to leave. They sit outside, waiting for a bus that never comes.





